g.text: Calm as a night. The dark blue of the night signifies the calmness in my soul
Fluid and adaptive as water. Blue of water symbolises the flexibility of mind.

text.tspan: The green leaves are a symbol of life. It suggests the creative spirit
in me and my heart that is full of life.
The logo ssymbolises my life force. The colours plays with the concept of calmness, creativity and life in
leaves also suggests the urge for growth and perfection.
